SONiC Data Directory
====================

This directory contains SONiC runtime data and configuration.

Files
-----

sonic-version.txt
  Version identifier for the SONiC image, created during image build.

config_db.json
  SONiC configuration database, bind-mounted into systemd-nspawn container at /etc/sonic/config_db.json.
  Created by setup-sonic script from /etc/hotstack-sonic/config_db.json or defaults.

bgpd.conf
  FRR BGP daemon configuration, bind-mounted into systemd-nspawn container at /etc/frr/bgpd.conf.
  Created by setup-sonic script from /etc/hotstack-sonic/bgpd.conf.

ospfd.conf
  FRR OSPF daemon configuration, bind-mounted into systemd-nspawn container at /etc/frr/ospfd.conf.
  Created by setup-sonic script from /etc/hotstack-sonic/ospfd.conf.

admin_ssh/
  Directory containing SSH authorized_keys for the admin user.
  Bind-mounted read-only into systemd-nspawn container at /home/admin/.ssh.
